description: The ripped Gymnast (0-1) takes on season veteran Dragon (11-3). The Gymnast is no push over, often powering herself out of tough holds, so her strength totally surprised the Dragon. However, as always, experience wins over muscle. It's so hot watching Wenona's ripped muscular body succumb to the talents of the Dragon. In RD4 the Dragon fucks the hell out of our flexible gymnast, a fucking she will not soon forget.
title: The Gymnast vs. The Dragon
